{
  "id": "vvH4SR2B",
  "slug": "what-is-stone-(colorful-caves)",
  "title": "What is 'Stone'? (Colorful Caves)",
  "description": "Okay, but really what is 'Stone'? What kind of stone? Let's add a bit of spice to the existing caves, vanilla style!",
  "body": "<p><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/NsMG1fC/What-Is-Stone.png\" alt=\"Logo\" width=\"1905\" height=\"589\" data-mce-src=\"https://i.ibb.co/NsMG1fC/What-Is-Stone.png\"></p><hr><p><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/NxTmwZb/About.png\" alt=\"About this Mod\" width=\"700\" height=\"216\" data-mce-src=\"https://i.ibb.co/NxTmwZb/About.png\"></p><hr><p><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">I've always found it weird that Minecraft just has a block called 'Stone'. What a generic term, and you're using it to cover so many different types of stone.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\" data-mce-style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">This is <strong>not</strong> doing real caves justice.</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\" data-mce-style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/1nLybgF/Screenshot-2023-05-23-193840.png\" alt=\"Image1\" width=\"400\" height=\"214\" data-mce-src=\"https://i.ibb.co/1nLybgF/Screenshot-2023-05-23-193840.png\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/DgC97XQ/Screenshot-2023-05-22-233455.png\" alt=\"image2\" width=\"400\" height=\"217\" data-mce-src=\"https://i.ibb.co/DgC97XQ/Screenshot-2023-05-22-233455.png\"></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\" data-mce-style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 24px;\">To fix this, we replaced all stone blocks with real life variants!&nbsp;</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Not only that, but badlands biomes get a minor overhaul with new blocks replacing most terracotta blocks!</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Now, there are a few potential issues with this mod. Luckily, I have done my best to tackle them all:</span></p><div class=\"spoiler\"><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 18px;\">- I can't craft things with these modded blocks! How am I supposed to get stone?</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 18px;\">I have added Forge tags that should allow you to craft stone tools, furnaces, etc. For other recipes, you can convert stone variants into cobblestone by placing 4 in your crafting inventory.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/jJ77S1Q/Screenshot-2023-04-29-162927.png\" alt=\"Crafting Recipe\" width=\"300\" height=\"213\" data-mce-src=\"https://i.ibb.co/jJ77S1Q/Screenshot-2023-04-29-162927.png\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 18px;\">- There are way too many blocks and it's clogging up my inventory!</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Once again, you can convert groups of any 4 stone variants into cobblestone using your crafting inventory. Additionally, you could use bundles, backpack mods, chests, or shulker boxes to store your blocks if you don't want to convert them.</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p></div><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 24px;\">You have full permission to use this mod in your modpack(s)! Credit is appreciated ^^</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Now with Excavated Variants Compatibility!</span></p><div class=\"spoiler\"><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 18px;\">In your globalresources folder, do the following:</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 18px;\">- create a folder (the name doesn't matter)</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 18px;\">- in this folder, create a folder named 'excavated_variants'</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 18px;\">- in this folder, create a folder named 'what_is_stone'</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 18px;\">- in this folder, create a folder named 'variants'</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 18px;\">- add this file to the folder:&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1RavcQrpKi72DZtyg-1-hahw0IX50vPOH/view?usp=share_link\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-mce-href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1RavcQrpKi72DZtyg-1-hahw0IX50vPOH/view?usp=sharing\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/1RavcQrpKi72DZtyg-1-hahw0IX50vPOH/view?usp=sharing</a></span></span></p></div><p>&nbsp;</p><hr><p><img style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\" src=\"https://i.ibb.co/c3GF7T3/Planned-Features.png\" alt=\"Planned Features\" width=\"700\" height=\"216\" data-mce-src=\"https://i.ibb.co/c3GF7T3/Planned-Features.png\" data-mce-style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"></p><hr><p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\" data-mce-style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">This mod is far from perfect, but I do plan to improve it in several ways:</span></span></p><div class=\"spoiler\"><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\" data-mce-style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">- Integrate BlockSwap mod or something similar to fully replace stone (world gen may still produce stone in rare instances)</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\" data-mce-style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">- Add more decorative building blocks (polished, brick, chiseled variants + stairs &amp; slabs)</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\" data-mce-style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">- Add cobblestone counterparts to some blocks</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\" data-mce-style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">- Add more stone variants</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\" data-mce-style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">- Remake some textures</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\" data-mce-style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">- Add ores/alloys w/compatibility for other mods</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\" data-mce-style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">- Separate furnace variant mod with compatibility for other mods, including this one</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\" data-mce-style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">- Port/Backport to other versions, likely 1.18.2, 1.19.4, or 1.16.5 (Leave a comment so I know what's in the highest demand!)</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\" data-mce-style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">- Fabric port (Maybe)</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\" data-mce-style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">- Add compatibility to other mods, including (sorted high to low priority):</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\" data-mce-style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 14px;\">- Excavated Variants</span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\" data-mce-style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; - Any decoration mod with Stone decor in it</span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\" data-mce-style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; - Vertical Slabs Compat (I find this obsolete when the Additional Placements mod exists)</span></span></span></p></div><p>&nbsp;</p><hr><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\" data-mce-style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/HP4rTpj/What-Is-Stone-1.png\" alt=\"Credits\" width=\"700\" height=\"216\" data-mce-src=\"https://i.ibb.co/HP4rTpj/What-Is-Stone-1.png\"></span></span></span></p><hr><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\" data-mce-style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 18px;\">- The creators of the&nbsp;<a title=\"Unearthed Mod\" href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/unearthed\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-mce-href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/unearthed\">Unearthed Mod,</a>&nbsp;for being a huge inspiration for me</span></span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\" data-mce-style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 18px;\">- The developers of MCreator, for providing an insanely helpful tool</span></span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\" data-mce-style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 18px;\">- All of you, for downloading my mod :D</span></span></span></span></p><hr><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\" data-mce-style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/yFhRDv4/Suggestions.png\" alt=\"Suggestions\" width=\"700\" height=\"216\" data-mce-src=\"https://i.ibb.co/yFhRDv4/Suggestions.png\"></span></span></span></span></p><hr><p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Please leave suggestions in the issues tab, your feedback and ideas are of high value to me!</span></p>",
